  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 6th level, you gain the ability to cloak yourself in a fey magic that makes others want to serve you. As a bonus action, you cast command, without expending a spell slot, and you take on an appearance of unearthly beauty for 1 minute or until your concentration ends (as if you were concentrating on a spell). During this time, you can cast command as a bonus action on each of your turns, without expending a spell slot.</p><p>Any creature charmed by you automatically fails its saving throw against the command you cast with this feature.</p><p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a spell slot of 2nd level or higher to use this again.</p>",
